flowchart LR
    A[Privileged action in any feature] --> B[Audit client emit]
    B --> C[Validate required fields]
    C --> D[Compute event hash + chain hash]
    D --> E[Persist to immutable audit store]
    E --> F[Async indexer for search]
    E --> G[Anomaly detection feed]
    G --> H[Risk + ops alerts on anomalies]
    F --> I[Per-seller audit log UI]
    F --> J[Pikshipp ops console search]
